title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Toulouse landmarks - version 0.1
description:
In this addon spotlight we will look at the Toulouse landmarks package which has been released today on flightsim.to. It contains 17 POI's which have been updated to more photo realistic.

The latest version of the landmark package can be downloaded from flightsim.to:
https://flightsim.to/file/23394/place-du-capitole-and-other-landmarks-for-toulouse
